    <h1>Innocence Project in North Carolina</h1>


  <p>The conditions of jails and detentions throughout the country are something of concern to many, throughout this investigative project, we took a look at what inmates have to say about their treatment and living conditions, worked with the Inside-Outside Coallition, and took a look at the work of the Innocence Project (a national organization that focuses on releasing wronglfully accused inmates). </p>

